{
  "id": 7422,
  "name": "Ancient Sacred Mountain",
  "desc": "<p>Before the descendants of the various tribes learned to record their history with woven scrolls, the ancient and proud nobility had already built a magnificent holy city here, scorning the land that those feeble slaves knew as \"Natlantea.\" However, the vast empire that prided itself on its power has long since perished in battle. Only a lonely tomb remains of that mighty city.</p>",
  "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/6fdb6cce9a5cce40096dce9c2672feba_7641303426493271828.png",
