    {
      "id": "71",
      "name": "Gallery",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/6720fc8f34741f1cdd09918df845dea1_5467966734364008620.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>An ancient city once sealed by a fragile oath, stirring feebly like sun-bleached bones rattling in the wind. What fateful conclusion will be set in motion by its final death throes?</p>",
                "key": "Once-Sealed Ancient City"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/07572b5fa339baa6bdda00d5a2e02ed3_3325317776300820289.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>It is said that a mighty ancient race once gained the knowledge they needed by submerging themselves in Phlogiston-rich flaming pools. It is also said that a weak and feeble race once attempted to do the same, only to be met by failure. Ultimately, it was a once benevolent sage who gave them the means to endure the knowledge they sought.</p>",
                "key": "Fiery Flowing Sea of Sentience"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/a5701e3c21f3169d0b0f151b3dcc71ad_1707393286574214491.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Golden runes divide light into multiple forms. Phlogiston drawn by a mighty power serves as a vessel in countless layers. Constructed stars float in the palm of a colossal hand.</p>",
                "key": "Condensed Altar"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/ea9ba83b7cadbad510164c0783ce3e5c_6476254617485015374.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>A meeting hall in prosperous times where dragons once crafted innumerable arcane arts and mechanisms. When their master departed, it became a place of judgment where dragon cast down dragon.</p>",
                "key": "Court of the Dragons"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/949d92524f4e06cf040d4f15f93d78a1_7694147058907219771.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The heart of the Sacred Mountain, hidden deep within its depths, and a hollow in the great dragon itself. Chosen of Dragons, return the shadow in the eye, and call forth the Sacred Flame to cleanse the world!</p>",
                "key": "A Hollow in the Heart"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/42b539508d495cd8583e8cd56d500363_6820106533927617243.png",
                "imgDesc": "",
                "key": "Locations Map"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/0ccd26d005d6d9437c325c1883b911b0_2492678187899234687.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Dragons' Residence, corrupted by the Abyss.</p>",
                "key": "Locations Map"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/29/237301566/6def56d9937048c0ec96a0786dd08a99_3096644685198687333.png",
